body:
Tyrus makes me hype

Now I know how other people are like hype about their fandoms and ships and keep them to themselves. This is a normal generalization I would use to describe me. But not on this faithful day. I was at my school’s GSA meeting and we were on the topic of gays in media. I wasn’t going to say Andi Mack initially because one my whole branding here and at school is Disney lover Molly and two is because I wasn’t fully awake. So, before I even thought about Andi Mack someone else said it. And before long I flipped out so hard that I fell out of my desk. This person however didn’t even imply Tyrus they just meant Cyrus but I went off. Being I hold a lot of Tyrus knowledge I started spitting out facts one after another until I was forced to stop talking. And this is the story of the time I flipped out over Tyrus

Does he even realise he has a crush? Will Buffy play a part in all of this? Will TJ be the one to admit it first? Will it be one Cyrus-centric episode or will it span multiple episodes with Andi drama in between? Will they use the term ‘boyfriend’ or just say ‘together’ ???
